id: pm-8d00
title: "Add MCP pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health integration tests"
description: "The MCP integration test suite (tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts, mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts) has solid coverage of pm_run, pm_search, pm_create, and pm_update. However pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, and pm_health have minimal or no MCP-specific integration test coverage. These are the highest-value MCP tools for agents: pm_context is the primary orientation tool, pm_plan drives structured agent work, pm_contracts is the machine-readable SDK surface, and pm_health is the self-repair entry point."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 2
tags[4]: "area:tests",coverage,integration,mcp
created_at: "2026-06-07T10:05:57.474Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-07T10:15:44.493Z"
author: audit-docs-tests-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- At least one integration test per tool (pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health) that:\n- calls the tool via the MCP handshake test harness\n- validates the compact-by-default output projection\n- validates key response shape (e.g. pm_context returns item array; pm_health returns ok boolean)"
parent: pm-u9d0
risk: medium
confidence: high
body: "## Context\nGrepped tests/integration/ for pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health:\n- pm_context: only 1 hit, in test-all-command.spec.ts (pm_context_mode metadata, not the tool itself)\n- pm_contracts: 0 dedicated MCP test hits in integration/\n- pm_plan: 0 MCP integration test hits\n- pm_health: 0 MCP integration test hits\n\nAll four tools are registered in src/mcp/server.ts but their MCP dispatch paths are not integration-tested.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- At least one integration test per tool (pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health) that:\n  - calls the tool via the MCP handshake test harness\n  - validates the compact-by-default output projection\n  - validates key response shape (e.g. pm_context returns item array; pm_health returns ok boolean)\n\n## Evidence\ntests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts; tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts; grep results for pm_context/pm_contracts/pm_plan/pm_health in tests/"
